         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Beechworth Athenaeum ¶ 1st May 1862 ¶ Dr. Mueller ¶ Dear Sir, ¶  ¶ I have very great pleasure — complying with the wish of the President — (G. B. ¶  ¶ Kerford ¶ Kerferd?Certainly Kerferd. Can MS give ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">62.05.01</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From William Morton</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">V62/2978, unit 749, VPRS 1189/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Beechworth Athenaeum</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1st May 1862</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have very great pleasure — complying with the wish of the President — (G. B.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">Kerford</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">Kerferd?</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">Certainly Kerf</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">rd. Can MS give benefit of doubt?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Esqr. J. P.) of this Institute — in writing you for the purpose of asking: whether you can grant the boon of a copy of your lately published &amp; highly valued work to this Institute?<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Presumably B62.03.03.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You must readily perceive that situated as we are, so far inland, that we lack many advantages which those situated nearer Melbourne possess; and the only way we have of presenting our interest is by letter, which is necessarily a very imperfect method for producing an impression.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am sure, however, that you will appreciate our position, &amp; will generously aid us when you can.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The request was enclosed with M<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to J. O'Shanassy, 3 May 1862.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Can you advise us as to the best means we can adopt in order to secure copies of the "Transactions of The Royal Society."?<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Presumably the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Transactions of the Royal Society of Victoria</seg>. The<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Transactions</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was not printed between vol.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>5 (1861) and vol.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>6 issued May 1865<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Editor's preface, vol.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>6, pp. v-vi).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Apologizing for making such demands on your generosity &amp; courtesy</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I am</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Very Sincerely Yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>William Morton<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Not further identified.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Curator of The Beechworth Athenaeum</p>
         </div>
